<headline>Special Weather Statement issued December 26 at 4:32PM MST  by NWS GreatFalls</headline>
<description>...Blowing snow causes low visibility through Monida Pass in
southeastern Beaverhead County through 600 PM MST...
Caution is advised for those traveling through Monida Pass, as gusty
winds to 30 mph are causing reduced visibility in blowing snow.
Locations impacted include...
Monida and Monida Pass.
MAX HAIL SIZE...0.00 IN
MAX WIND GUST...&lt;30 MPH</description>
